<D>__{i don't believe it! lasorda's calling up the "old man" to pinch run in the biggest clutch situation this season! they say the veteran's lost a step or two. but if i were you, i'd get ready for some fireworks.}
<C>__{the crowd}
<A>__{is on its feet as 40 year old benny "the jet" rodriguez takes over third base from the player already there. they shake hands on the exchange. the 3rd base coach walks over to the jet. pats him on the back.}
