<A>__{settles.}
<C>__{the jet}
<A>__{leads off. eleven steps.}
<C>__{the pitcher}
<A>__{fires to 3rd again. the jet gets back.}
<C>__{the jet}
<A>__{leads off again. twelve steps. the pitch strike. the catcher tosses it back. just then... ...the jet moves. so fast that no one knows he's gone till it's too damn late. the pitcher awkwardly throws home. the catcher wipes the baseline. too late... ...the dust clears. the umpire eagle wings the air.}
<C>__{umpire}
<D>__{safe! safe! safe!}
<A>__{the tag missed by two feet. it's all over. the crowd jumps to its feet. the dodger dugout is all over the jet.}
